    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255100/extras/dc06d0a5d73762aa6ead43b8fc481723.avif?t=1753454187\" width=610 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this story, you will control <strong>Riley</strong>, a girl who has noticed a grotesque change in her <strong>mother</strong>’s behavior over time, putting her in various challenging situations from which you must help her escape unharmed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to uncover what <strong>Mom</strong> is hiding?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255100/extras/32423630c1939400d0a3354d3735b136.avif?t=1753454187\" width=610 height=130 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a <strong>disturbing</strong> <strong>atmosphere</strong> of terror as you solve puzzles within the house and explore other maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring pixel art graphics inspired by classic horror works.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark narrative filled with secrets surrounding your own mother.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The use of headphones is highly recommended for an immersive experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience around 2 hours of horror, packed with a diverse range of maps and puzzles.                                  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >                                       WHY ISN'T MOM SLEEPING?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255100/extras/ac23555dc3649b9dfbb7d2f5faf7ab92.poster.avif?t=1753454187\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255100/extras/ac23555dc3649b9dfbb7d2f5faf7ab92.webm?t=1753454187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3255100/extras/ac23555dc3649b9dfbb7d2f5faf7ab92.mp4?t=1753454187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
